MAKEUP NOT SITTING RIGHT?
CHECK THESE 5 PREPPING MISTAKES..👇🏻

Mistake #1:
Skipping moisturiser 💧
Even oily skin needs hydration — dry skin makes foundation cling to patches.

Mistake #2:
Not cleansing properly 🧼
Leftover oil or dirt = makeup slides off faster and looks uneven.

Mistake #3:
Applying primer on damp skin ⚠️
Let your skincare absorb fully — rushing can cause pilling and uneven texture.

Mistake #4:
Using the wrong primer 🎯
Silicone primer on dry skin? Hydrating primer on oily skin? Match your primer to your skin type!

Mistake #5:
Skipping lip prep 💋
Dry, cracked lips ruin even the best lipstick — scrub + balm is a must before any lip product.

POV: Makeup Artist Trap 🚩
Here are red flags every bride should watch out for before booking a makeup artist:
❌ No trial offered - off course one can charge for the same 
❌ Over-edited or fake portfolio
❌ Poor hygiene
❌ no clear communication
❌ Doesn’t ask your skin type/preferences
❌ No contract or clear terms
❌ Pushy with their own style
❌ Demands full payment upfront
